# meancommerce

*A MEAN stack based E-Commerce Platform*
*http://www.meancommerce.com*


## Table of Contents

  1. [Installation](#installation)
  2. [Configuration](#configuration)
  3. [Development](#development)
  4. [Production](#production)
  5. [License](#License)

## 1. Installation
  
  - $ git clone https://github.com/sifiumco/meancommerce.git
  - $ cd meancommerce
  - $ npm install

**[⬆ back to top](#table-of-contents)**


## 2. Configuration

  - Goto ./config/env/all.js, and make the necessary changes

**[⬆ back to top](#table-of-contents)**


## 3. Development

  - $ grunt
    Navigate to localhost:3000 in your browser to view the website

**[⬆ back to top](#table-of-contents)**


## 4. Production

  - $ NODE_ENV=production grunt build
    Make the site production ready
  - $ NODE_ENV=production node server.js
    Server started at port 3000



